864
00:43:21,326 --> 00:43:24,196
and some very severe
failure modes,


865
00:43:24,646 --> 00:43:26,366
and updating the
main database file


866
00:43:26,366 --> 00:43:29,446
in place has been somewhat
difficult to manage.


867
00:43:29,926 --> 00:43:32,836
So under WAL mode --
