903
00:45:11,116 --> 00:45:12,446
at the same SQLite store.


904
00:45:12,856 --> 00:45:16,086
And with this kind of setup you
have, you can basically have one


905
00:45:16,086 --> 00:45:19,656
of these coordinators doing
